{
  "id": "RAW_35e39b",
  "title": "Codex CLI 是 Claude Code 的最佳替代品和编程搭子",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247498780&idx=1&sn=26a7cfc14a5f3af5a1073b5b8e67070d",
  "date": "2025-09-02 06:20:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为各种各样的原因（包括且不限于太贵、太容易封号），小伙伴们一直在寻找Claude Code的替代品。 在过去两个月，我们测试过Kimi K2、GLM 4.5、Qwen Coder等等，它们的能力暂时比起Claude都有较大的差距。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在，我们终于找到了答案了！ 来自OpenAI 的Code CLI， 完美解决了我们的问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不仅如此，还有：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">今天，很可能是你正式放弃Cursor的第一天。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">OpenAI Code CLI的特点</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Code CLI官方提供VS Code的GUI插件，对小白友好（类似Cursor）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Code CLI背后的模型是ChatGPT-5，编码能力为第一梯队，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">除了做UI的能力不如Claude Code，其他都不比Claude Code弱</span>。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">幻觉比Claude Code低。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">速度比Claude Code快。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">国内用户使用，不容易封号。（仍然需要魔法上网）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">比Claude Code便宜、比Cursor便宜。我们只需要订阅ChatGPT Plus (每月$20美元) ，就能够支撑日常使用。 &nbsp;至于Cursor，虽然它也每个$20美元，但重度使用者三五天就能用完一整月的限额。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"color:#ff6827;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">算法、数学等复杂编程能力，Code CLI 比 Claude Code 更强。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">我将会使用到Claude Code的场景</span></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有场景，我会<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">默认</span>使用Claude Code</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">UI类工作，Claude Code是唯一选择</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">我将会使用Codex的场景</span></span></p>\n    <p></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">复杂编程场景，如：复现论文、修改算法、优化推理框架等。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"color:#ff6827;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">帮助Claude Code做代码审核，挑刺</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">小型修改，可用Codex VS Code插件代替Cursor。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">Codex CLI能完全代替Claude Code吗？</span></span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color:#ff6827&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">对很多新手来说，可以。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">对我来说，暂时还不能。但是我可以让Codex成为Claude Code的编程搭子。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">想知道为啥不能？推荐你听我的播客，里面有讲我使用Claude Code的高级玩法</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;background-color: transparent;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498770&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0b252c03df0fbac24d6aec1dc15bf6cc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致 | 对话刘小排\" data-itemshowtype=\"8\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;\">揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致 | 对话刘小排</span></a></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">Codex &nbsp;安装方法</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">官方提供了两种安装，我推荐两个方式一起上。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">1. 安装CLI&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">只需要在命令行中执行：</span></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">npm</span>&nbsp;install -g&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">@openai</span>/codex</span></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">根据引导，使用ChatGPT账号进行登录</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015088\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43683083511777304\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"934\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3456273&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFO6FOU6DiaOcFK2VrfUdcHEJWticKnoYmTfY7cMHlXlR3HazRicvs1FcXicd3t4tsialMuSghRE6244ibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用方式和Claude Code非常类似。下面简单演示一下</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">/model&nbsp;</span>命令选择模型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">我的经验： 只要不是做界面，gpt-5 high就是最强的编码模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015090\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2898148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ea74ccd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFO6FOU6DiaOcFK2VrfUdcHEyE8rx3SzbibAlqPZDsouXC9dw2BGTiaoUEmx66APpx0tQEFPGWTNyJMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在你的项目中，使用&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">/init&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">命令，可以初始化项目。&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">&nbsp;Claude Code 会帮你写一个CLAUDE.md 文件， &nbsp;Codex Cli 会写Agents.md 文件， 名字不同，作用相同。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015094\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.09513742071881606\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37572c23&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFO6FOU6DiaOcFK2VrfUdcHE3ciaEOicThQJaiceXcrFvf3bib9CHFY8BemqvbeWC4WZO5MTcKJRgcSIlA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">2. 安装VS Code插件</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">打开VS Code的插件市场，搜索Codex。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意不要安装错了，有好几个山寨版。请认准下图红框这个，开发者是OpenAI， 这才是官方版。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015124\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1786492374727668\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"918\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5d96fbb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGdRI2tCiaMWT4C5qGqZrQib0exM1MdibYu7b6X0pvhZoRibQc4Vib99fMLRUfxVMgic4jmjOicfkAcYmFuA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装完成后，你的VS Code侧边栏最下面会出现一个OpenAI的logo，点击它，就可以进行聊天了。看下图右侧。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">今天，很可能是你正式放弃Cursor的第一天。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015126\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5833333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b9803d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGdRI2tCiaMWT4C5qGqZrQib0vENzA81jvxrVDpVBI2crkNaibKyuBHnj7leQTwasGZswTTQrgrtO9tQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"3 7 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-weight:bold;font-size:24px;\">Codex CLI的一些缺点</span></span></p>\n   <div data-pm-slice=\"3 6 []\">\n    <p></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Codex CLI的用户体验比较糟糕，比起Claude Code有差距。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">与Claude Code 相比，Codex CLI还并不是一个完善的、自主的、能够比得上实习生的Agent</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">例如，我让Codex CLI和Claude Code自己研究，这俩货到底谁好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这道题，Claude Code答得好太多了，无论是展现形式上还是回答质量上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">请看截图，高下立现。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">图1是Claude Code的回答</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015095\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0222222222222221\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d53feebe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFO6FOU6DiaOcFK2VrfUdcHEK1ia7z2poJicO06UyWCwjMaG1PUM5bLN5zz0IDgvLDNBnPJ381aCFCGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">图2是Codex Cli的回答</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015096\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e8617068&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFO6FOU6DiaOcFK2VrfUdcHEzkh4rfK0n1pn6d62GRnRPJXylcVvVjKBxLmrW5miaiaxf5pEqO6GLtaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">Codex CLI做Claude Code的编程搭子</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过连续3天的使用，我对Codex CLI的优点、缺点、特点有了足够的了解。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我发现，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">对我而言，Codex CLI最好的使用方法是： 让它成为Claude Code的编程搭子</span>。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何用Codex做Claude Code的编程搭子？</span></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"3 7 []\">\n   <div data-pm-slice=\"3 6 []\">\n    <p></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">以Claude Code为主，让Codex挑刺</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"color:#ff6827;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">讨论方案和审核代码阶段，两者左右互搏，直到达成一致</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以在项目中，同时打开Claude Code和Codex。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 让Claude Code出方案</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 把方案发给Codex进行评审，挑刺</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 把Codex挑刺的内容发给Claude Code，问它是否同意 （往往会同意）。如果同意，开始补充计划；如果不同意，把为什么不同意，复制给Codex，问问它的看法。&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">两者对方案达成共识后，让Claude Code写代码</span>。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">5. 让Codex对代码进行Review，重复步骤3</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">6.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">两者对代码达成共识后，提交代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面简单演示一下</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景： 我让Claude Code完成了creem支付的接入，改动比较大，想让Codex进行检查。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我告诉Codex一个git提交的ID (Commit ID)，让它自己去检查。</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个git提交8fcae5eaac3f8a022025a82c1330de4f99bf4268 是我写的creem支付代码，请你检查，结合creem官方文档，看看我们写对没，是否有疏漏</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015128\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.825\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7122be4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGdRI2tCiaMWT4C5qGqZrQib0knAFAfObHvS1xEBINK2hgjRK7DGyR9a1DibQcXZo10WQJ3BcLtQKSxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">十分钟后，得到了审核意见，发给Claude Code。</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是别人对git提交8fcae5eaac3f8a022025a82c1330de4f99bf4268&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 的代码审核,你同意它的看法吗? 请你独立思考,多上网搜索调研&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下图一目了然：左边是Codex右边是Claude Code</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015129\" data-ratio=\"0.4546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ebaefc3a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGdRI2tCiaMWT4C5qGqZrQib0e47jZjjtDsibUgx7via5ibt5IWKQQuxohOGAtJF7NhqzFvEXibp2g3ibprQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code正在对审核意见内容进行逐一核实</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015130\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3962962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=885612c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGdRI2tCiaMWT4C5qGqZrQib0TBVBycdiaQHANuNldY84ics1owua0ibibIqFEGMzdMiczB9fofMdKVKYnhw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code同意了一部分Codex的观点，并且做了一些补充</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015131\" data-ratio=\"0.39814814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7237607f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGdRI2tCiaMWT4C5qGqZrQib0HVxNnWMFpBDWiaADQwRG9Noq0aq5icJjAauBCWQDvaa4X12SChPrFsiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来我让他俩‘左右互搏’几轮，直到完全达成一致！</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么样，好玩吧？ 赶快去玩起来吧！期待你的反馈！</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细介绍了 OpenAI 的 Codex CLI 作为 Claude Code 的有力编程搭子和部分场景的替代品，尤其在复杂编程和代码审核方面表现出色，并提供了详细的使用策略和安装指南。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细介绍了 OpenAI 的 Codex CLI 作为 Claude Code 的有力编程搭子和部分场景的替代品，尤其在复杂编程和代码审核方面表现出色，并提供了详细的使用策略和安装指南。",
  "summary": "本文旨在为寻找 Claude Code 替代品的开发者提供解决方案，重点介绍了 OpenAI 的 Codex CLI。作者刘小排指出，Codex CLI 基于 ChatGPT-5 模型，在编码能力上与 Claude Code 处于第一梯队，尤其在算法、数学等复杂编程任务上表现更强，且幻觉更低、速度更快、成本更低廉，对于国内用户而言也更不易封号。文章详细对比了 Codex CLI 与 Claude Code 的优劣，指出 Codex CLI 在 UI 类工作和用户体验方面仍有不足，但其官方提供的 VS Code 插件极大地降低了使用门槛。最核心的观点是提出了“Codex CLI 作为 Claude Code 的编程搭子”的创新使用策略，通过让两者在方案设计和代码审核阶段进行“左右互搏”，互相评审和补充，从而显著提升代码质量和开发效率。文章还提供了 Codex CLI 的安装方法（CLI 和 VS Code 插件）以及具体的使用演示，并通过实际案例展示了双 AI 协作进行代码审核的流程。",
